                     <interp inst="t18001203-61-off324" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18001203-61-off324" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18001203-61-cd325" type="crimeDate">16th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18001203-61-off324 t18001203-61-cd325"></join>, two pounds weight of flour, value 10d. three loaves of bread, value 3d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18001203-61-victim387" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     May
                  <interp inst="t18001203-61-victim387" type="surname" value="May"></interp>
